{"tid":362663,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"上市數月任天堂 Switch 機身微彎問題持續","createTime":"2017-08-17T05:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T12:20:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"095ff8411322aa87a85971b38809f83caa2d08d8","tid":362663,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:59:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">八月 17, 2017</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/0817-4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F0817-4c.jpg&h=235855ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任天堂 Switch 上市至今已經有幾個月，雖然未有出現嚴重的質量問題和事故，但就曾出現過懷疑電池輕微膨脹的報告。另一小問題則是手機機身有微微彎曲的情況，外國討論區 Reddit、NeoGAF，甚至社交平台 Twitter 都有 Switch 用戶報告類似情況，但未算十分嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/0817-4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F0817-4a.jpg&h=617d52d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從 Twitter 見到不少彎曲個案的苦主，他們的 Switch 的彎曲情況其實頗為明顯，肉眼都可以見到。開始時有用戶估計情況只是推出初期才有的現象，認為是任天堂趕著上市，忽略品質管理的結果。不過問題不但未有隨著上市時間而有所改善，近期就連日本用戶都開始投訴，Switch 出現彎曲的狀況，有個別個案甚至因為機身彎曲，屏幕的角出現突出的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於嚴重缺貨的日本來說，用戶對這機身彎曲十分苦惱，因為能夠買到 Switch 十分難得，很多人不想為此退貨重新等候。導致機身彎曲的原因至今還未查明，而任天堂亦未有公開回應，用戶只能自行決定是否退貨或要求維修，或是忍受微微彎曲的機身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/0817-4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F0817-4b.jpg&h=eff25532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/08/17/nintendo-switch-bend/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2Fnintendo-switch-bend%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=aAacu4mfd3UTEkJ5WZj%2BeROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=551f1c89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/08/17/nintendo-switch-bend/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"5eab332c2cd1fcf8e71380ec7bcf0cc074f85bf2","tid":362663,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:08:14.000Z","msg":"屌啦，之前我買部3ds啲柒甩到我成隻手都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc4f8cddea1de3d35ba78884e860b38f95a4cd1","tid":362663,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2f523acb6d1c469ffd265e62004d41893f3081","tid":362663,"uid":29246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"原來個Mon真係會噉樣凸起, 我都衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f17c2dfdea628f8e0b7da13c1b07b072731ad6","tid":362663,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:01:27.000Z","msg":"日本仔真係陰功<br />\n機又買唔到 仲有機會係彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397d20da1631325d48a8058a4b654c0bafe0daa7","tid":362663,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b44eec95453f070c12cec72ce66468c9501db5","tid":362663,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:45:27.000Z","msg":"日本大把細路為左部電子垃圾排隊買遊戲機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好篤住佢地個頭黎笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba28fcad5e7527e512a7181c5eeb7923b3e1074","tid":362663,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d035e0a80ff0e361a4dedf7529e5af978250df0","tid":362663,"uid":34550,"like":0,"disl